data.name: ReadCsePerson1
data.value: select top(1) NUMB, TYPE, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, UNEMPLOYMENT_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON where NUMB = @numb

data.name: ReadCsePerson2
data.value: select NUMB, TYPE, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, UNEMPLOYMENT_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON where UNEMPLOYMENT_IND = 'A'

data.name: ReadCsePerson3
data.value: select NUMB, TYPE, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, UNEMPLOYMENT_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON where UNEMPLOYMENT_IND = 'Y'

data.name: UpdateCsePerson1
data.value: update CKT_CSE_PERSON set LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, UNEMPLOYMENT_IND = @unemploymentInd where NUMB = @numb

data.name: UpdateCsePerson2
data.value: update CKT_CSE_PERSON set LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, UNEMPLOYMENT_IND = @unemploymentInd where NUMB = @numb

data.name: UpdateCsePerson3
data.value: update CKT_CSE_PERSON set LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, UNEMPLOYMENT_IND = @unemploymentInd where NUMB = @numb
